  "texts": [
    "For work specifying the amount of data used (either in the paper or through a repository), we consider the given value.",
    "For the rest, we calculate it by inspecting the actual dataset.",
    "16 In seven papers, no number of samples used was specified, so we contacted the authors for clarification.",
    "In the two cases where the authors did not respond, we assumed the entire split of a dataset was used.",
    "We calculated both the number of instances and the percentage of the considered split (or the whole dataset when applicable)."
